{"tid":432779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［不是第一次］北京：允許誰入境是中國主權","createTime":"2017-10-11T23:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T02:10:34.000Z","uid":41351,"like":6,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3f8a3b55396d8ff366ae9151afa3de157be60871","tid":432779,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T23:28:45.000Z","msg":"涉及香港回歸問題的《中英聯合聲明》實施30年，英國國會外交事務委員會早前公佈，會就《中英聯合聲明》頒佈30年的實施情況，到香港進行調查。中國表明不准許英國下議院議員到港，英國首相卡梅倫1日批評這是錯誤的決定，影響了中英外交關係。中國外交部發言人華春瑩則表示，允許誰入境，不允許誰入境，是中國的主權。<br />\n香港正爆發回歸之後最大型的爭取民主運動，而今年亦是《中英聯合聲明》實施30年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/9883\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Famparticle%2F9883&d=LQg54iOBw0XQMg%2FrxuC0ax4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=3eaf4f0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.thenewslens.com/amparticle/9883</a><br />\n支那政權想邊個入就邊個入<br />\n外交事務權不在香港到"},{"pid":"aa402af480c7d13f8ff81395dd4c8c8d3b4b09ca","tid":432779,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T23:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8072933123e7b0614046f89a18c8af80daee121a","tid":432779,"uid":2267,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T23:33:06.000Z","msg":"算唔算帶頭違反基本法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58718b102f0917546255cbcd6fefe339d435bda5","tid":432779,"uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T23:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算唔算帶頭違反基本法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本法外交，國防權利在中國<br />\n外國官員身分訪港，算係外交範圍"},{"pid":"76b9e09e4adf7c830bf338f3d0182b2448f1eb8d","tid":432779,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T23:35:45.000Z","msg":"借個位黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"h